{{> layout/header}}

<style>

    .table th, .table td {
        vertical-align: middle;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .table th {
        background-color: #c4d2d9;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .page-title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .rubric-table th {
        background-color: #c4d2d9;
    }

    .note {
        color: red;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }
</style>


<div class="container p-5">

    <div class="page-title">
        <h1>평가기준</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h5 class="section-title">※ 훈련목표</h5>
        <p>
            {{model.subjectPurpose}}
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h5 class="section-title">※ 교과목 및 세부내용</h5>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>교과목</th>
                <th>세부내용</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>{{model.subjectTitle}}</td>
                <td class="text-start">
                    {{#model.subjectElements}}
                        - {{.}}<br>
                    {{/model.subjectElements}}
                </td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h5 class="section-title">※ 루브릭(rubric) : 평가기준 요약</h5>
        <table class="table table-bordered rubric-table">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 15%">수행과제</th>
                <th style="width: 15%">평가기준</th>
                <th style="width: 35%">우수(100점)</th>
                <th style="width: 35%">미흡(60점)</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td rowspan="6">{{model.subjectTitle}}</td>
                <td>{{model.rubricFirst.subjectElement}}</td>
                <td>{{model.rubricFirst.questionPurpose}}</td>
                <td>{{model.rubricFirst.questionFail}}</td>
            </tr>

            {{#model.rubrics}}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{subjectElement}}</td>
                    <td>{{questionPurpose}}</td>
                    <td>{{questionFail}}</td>
                </tr>
            {{/model.rubrics}}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="note">
            ※ 소스코드 실행이 안될 시, 감점이 있음을 유의하세요.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{> layout/footer}}
